WEBVTT

17:02.950 --> 17:05.070 line:80%
-Yeah, we can't survive this.
-What are we supposed to do?

17:05.070 --> 17:05.909 line:80%
I also heard people

17:05.909 --> 17:08.960 line:80%
from the neighboring village went to kneel
at the county office to beg for mercy.

17:08.960 --> 17:09.869 line:80%
They knelt all day

17:09.869 --> 17:12.240 line:80%
but didn't even get to see the Magistrate.
